race.description: Ladbrokes Srm In Multis Max 150 Points Ht 2 H
race.comment: GENOVESE (2) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (19.86) at Capalaba. Yet to win at the journey but has run some good races. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Has winning claims on his best figures. GOOD LOOKIN' MAN (1) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. Key player on best and worth another try. BARNEY GOOGLE (3) comes here off a freshen-up and must be included.
